1
00:00:09,062 --> 00:00:09,858
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,202 --> 00:00:18,830
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,873 --> 00:00:22,034
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,710 --> 00:00:26,372
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:30,108
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,918 --> 00:00:34,910
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,688 --> 00:00:38,680
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:44,560
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,333 --> 00:00:49,233
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,302 --> 00:00:51,327
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:51,404 --> 00:00:53,463
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,841 --> 00:00:56,604
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,676 --> 00:00:58,576
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,645 --> 00:01:01,079
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,982 --> 00:01:09,546
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,523 --> 00:01:13,151
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:16,793
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,634 --> 00:01:23,067
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,538 --> 00:01:26,937
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:41,498 --> 00:01:42,624
Darn it!

21
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:46,227
Where'd he attack from?!
Is it the clones?

22
00:01:49,273 --> 00:01:51,468
Where's the real body?!

23
00:01:52,142 --> 00:01:54,508
It's useless for you to even attempt
following with your eyes.

24
00:01:54,812 --> 00:01:57,178
I absolutely will not be caught.

25
00:01:57,514 --> 00:02:00,074
Humph. Shadow Clone Jutsu!

26
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:00,912
Don't!

27
00:02:13,063 --> 00:02:15,588
This is a teleportation Jutsu that

28
00:02:15,666 --> 00:02:18,658
uses mirrors that can
reflect only my image.

29
00:02:19,036 --> 00:02:20,901
Watching you from the speed I move,

30
00:02:20,971 --> 00:02:23,565
it almost seems as if
you aren't moving at all...

31
00:02:25,009 --> 00:02:25,976
<i>I knew it!</i>

32
00:02:26,610 --> 00:02:28,908
Is that Jutsu...
the Kekkei Genkai?!

33
00:02:31,448 --> 00:02:33,473
Kekkei... Genkai?

34
00:02:34,385 --> 00:02:36,751
It's the same type as
my Sharingan...

35
00:02:37,388 --> 00:02:38,480
Then...!

36
00:02:38,689 --> 00:02:39,553
That's right...

37
00:02:40,124 --> 00:02:43,924
It's impossible even for me
to copy that Jutsu...

38
00:02:44,962 --> 00:02:47,157
And there's no way to destroy
that Jutsu, either!

39
00:02:51,936 --> 00:02:52,766
Darn it...

40
00:02:54,104 --> 00:02:56,629
So... What?!

41
00:02:57,408 --> 00:03:00,206
I can't die here yet.

42
00:03:00,711 --> 00:03:04,078
'Cause I have a dream
that I must turn into reality...

43
00:03:04,148 --> 00:03:07,777
The dream to have my strength
recognized by everyone in the village...

44
00:03:07,851 --> 00:03:10,149
and become the Hokage!

45
00:03:11,689 --> 00:03:12,678
<i>Dream...</i>

46
00:03:15,726 --> 00:03:21,255
I, for the sake of my dream.
And you, for the sake of your dream.

47
00:03:22,333 --> 00:03:23,857
Please don't hold it against me.

48
00:03:24,802 --> 00:03:27,236
I want to protect someone
special to me...

49
00:03:28,205 --> 00:03:32,107
I work for the sake of that person,
I fight for that person,

50
00:03:32,609 --> 00:03:34,941
and I want to make that
person's dream a reality...

51
00:03:35,312 --> 00:03:36,779
That's my dream.

52
00:03:37,114 --> 00:03:40,447
For the sake of that dream
I will completely become a Shinobi,

53
00:03:40,517 --> 00:03:43,077
and kill you guys!

54
00:03:51,695 --> 00:03:56,098
<i>Zero Visibility.</i>
<i>The Sharingan Shatters</i>

55
00:04:00,804 --> 00:04:04,934
Sasuke! Naruto!
Don't lose to a guy like that!

56
00:04:05,109 --> 00:04:07,577
Stop it, Sakura. Don't goad him!

57
00:04:08,012 --> 00:04:08,774
What?

58
00:04:09,413 --> 00:04:12,871
Even if there was a chance that
we could break that technique,

59
00:04:13,283 --> 00:04:16,252
they won't be able to defeat that boy.

60
00:04:17,688 --> 00:04:19,417
W-What do you mean?

61
00:04:22,326 --> 00:04:25,352
They don't have the mentality
to kill their feelings...

62
00:04:25,429 --> 00:04:27,693
and kill another person!

63
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:33,368
That boy really knows
the agony of being a Shinobi.

64
00:04:34,705 --> 00:04:36,570
He's different from Naruto and Sasuke.

65
00:04:37,141 --> 00:04:38,438
Exactly...

66
00:04:39,276 --> 00:04:45,237
No real Shinobi will come out of
a peace-addicted village like yours.

67
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:49,683
Because they are not able
to learn

68
00:04:49,753 --> 00:04:52,745
the most important "experience of killing"!

69
00:04:55,359 --> 00:04:56,223
Then...

70
00:04:56,427 --> 00:04:57,257
Then...

71
00:04:57,327 --> 00:04:59,591
What are we going to do, Sensei?!

72
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:05,892
<i>If I go over to</i>
<i>Naruto and Sasuke,</i>

73
00:05:05,969 --> 00:05:08,164
<i>Tazuna will be in danger.</i>

74
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,499
<i>Even if I try the Shadow Clones.</i>

75
00:05:15,446 --> 00:05:18,643
<i>He'll come to stop me with</i>
<i>his Water Clones.</i>

76
00:05:19,483 --> 00:05:21,542
I'll just be wasting Chakra.

77
00:05:22,419 --> 00:05:23,681
<i>Then...</i>

78
00:05:24,288 --> 00:05:26,813
I'm sorry but...

79
00:05:28,158 --> 00:05:31,025
I'm going to have to finish
this in an instant.

80
00:05:32,362 --> 00:05:33,386
Sharingan?!

81
00:05:35,532 --> 00:05:37,022
The Sharingan again?

82
00:05:37,234 --> 00:05:39,464
Such an unimaginative guy!

83
00:05:58,388 --> 00:05:59,412
Sensei!

84
00:06:06,230 --> 00:06:08,460
You might call me "an unimaginative guy,"

85
00:06:09,032 --> 00:06:12,331
but you are afraid of the Sharingan,
after all... Zabuza!

86
00:06:15,239 --> 00:06:17,434
The secret technique of a Shinobi...

87
00:06:17,541 --> 00:06:20,999
isn't something that you show
your opponent so many times.

88
00:06:21,378 --> 00:06:22,675
Be appreciative.

89
00:06:22,746 --> 00:06:26,978
You're the only who has had
the chance to see it twice...

90
00:06:28,018 --> 00:06:30,885
And there will be no third time...

91
00:06:32,956 --> 00:06:38,155
Even if you were able to defeat me,
you can't defeat Haku...

92
00:06:38,395 --> 00:06:39,327
What...?

93
00:06:43,267 --> 00:06:45,565
<i>Kakashi Sensei can't win?</i>

94
00:06:46,136 --> 00:06:48,764
<i>That boy in the mask is that strong?</i>

95
00:06:49,139 --> 00:06:52,666
Since he was a kid, I have been
painstakingly teaching him

96
00:06:52,743 --> 00:06:55,041
the battle techniques of the Ninja!

97
00:07:14,164 --> 00:07:17,497
All of my techniques.

98
00:07:21,071 --> 00:07:22,299
On top of that...

99
00:07:22,372 --> 00:07:25,307
he has been polishing up
his own skills as well!

100
00:07:28,612 --> 00:07:30,136
As a result...

101
00:07:30,514 --> 00:07:31,947
He has...

102
00:07:32,883 --> 00:07:36,046
no matter how unbelievably difficult
his predicament,

103
00:07:37,221 --> 00:07:39,655
been extremely successful.

104
00:07:42,926 --> 00:07:47,056
He has no "heart" and has
abandoned the notion of "life."

105
00:07:47,965 --> 00:07:50,798
He is a fighting machine
known as a Shinobi.

106
00:07:53,971 --> 00:07:56,838
Not only that,
his Jutsu surpasses mine!

107
00:07:57,641 --> 00:08:00,940
The terrifying ability of
the Kekkei Genkai.

108
00:08:02,412 --> 00:08:05,404
In other words,
I have acquired a sophisticated tool.

109
00:08:06,283 --> 00:08:09,684
Unlike the scrap you're
carrying around.

110
00:08:09,853 --> 00:08:13,584
I'm not one to be afraid just
because I failed once!

111
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:15,755
I'll do it as many times as it takes!

112
00:08:15,926 --> 00:08:17,553
The Shadow Clone Jutsu!

113
00:08:18,161 --> 00:08:18,855
Stop!

114
00:08:52,796 --> 00:08:54,286
W-What the hell is it...?!

115
00:08:57,934 --> 00:08:59,162
<i>I-It was just slight but...</i>

116
00:09:07,311 --> 00:09:09,370
<i>I could see the trails of his movements...</i>

117
00:09:10,113 --> 00:09:11,580
One more try!

118
00:09:13,617 --> 00:09:15,312
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

119
00:09:26,363 --> 00:09:29,389
Don't you understand that it's useless?

120
00:09:47,117 --> 00:09:48,880
<i>Just because I see the trail,</i>

121
00:09:48,952 --> 00:09:51,250
<i>doesn't mean that I can keep up</i>
<i>with his speed.</i>

122
00:09:57,094 --> 00:09:58,857
<i>The water...</i>
<i>is being repelled.</i>

123
00:10:01,898 --> 00:10:04,924
<i>But, what if that wasn't water...?</i>

124
00:10:07,204 --> 00:10:08,193
<i>All right...</i>

125
00:10:08,872 --> 00:10:10,430
<i>The next one is going</i>
<i>to be my one shot!</i>

126
00:10:12,242 --> 00:10:14,210
Just because a bunch of scrap
got together

127
00:10:14,277 --> 00:10:16,142
doesn't mean that
they can defeat Haku.

128
00:10:16,613 --> 00:10:19,707
He is...
He is the best tool!

129
00:10:19,783 --> 00:10:23,310
There's nothing boring than
a stranger bragging...

130
00:10:24,254 --> 00:10:26,882
It's about time...
I make my move.

131
00:10:27,257 --> 00:10:30,021
Now wait.
As long as we're talking...

132
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:32,651
Let me brag about another thing...

133
00:10:32,963 --> 00:10:33,793
Hmm?

134
00:10:34,965 --> 00:10:36,626
In the battle before,

135
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:41,127
I didn't just let you defeat me
like a fool.

136
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:01,218
<i>It's over...</i>

137
00:11:04,127 --> 00:11:05,924
Haku, who was hiding in the corner,

138
00:11:06,530 --> 00:11:10,159
was observing part of the battle.

139
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:12,297
Haku is quite smart.

140
00:11:12,803 --> 00:11:14,168
With his ability to analyze,

141
00:11:14,237 --> 00:11:19,140
he is able to plan a counterattack
after observing a technique just once.

142
00:11:20,744 --> 00:11:24,874
I've been anxious to copy your line.

143
00:11:28,351 --> 00:11:33,015
"I'll tell you now, but the same Jutsu
won't work on me twice."

144
00:11:33,256 --> 00:11:34,518
Was that it...?

145
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:40,455
Ninja Art, Hidden Mist Jutsu!

146
00:11:54,412 --> 00:11:58,007
Ninja Art, Hidden Mist Jutsu!

147
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,790
This is?!

148
00:12:20,738 --> 00:12:23,332
<i>What is this...?</i>
<i>This really thick fog?</i>

149
00:12:24,409 --> 00:12:25,933
<i>The visibility is close to z ero...</i>

150
00:12:26,411 --> 00:12:27,400
Sensei...!

151
00:12:30,448 --> 00:12:32,575
Sakura! Stay with Tazuna!

152
00:12:34,285 --> 00:12:35,252
<i>That's right.</i>

153
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:38,653
<i>I have to trust Sasuke,</i>
<i>Naruto and Kakashi Sensei right now...</i>

154
00:12:39,157 --> 00:12:41,284
And I should do what I can do!

155
00:12:42,327 --> 00:12:43,351
Huh?

156
00:12:43,728 --> 00:12:45,161
Oh! Sakura!

157
00:12:46,597 --> 00:12:49,794
Mr. Tazuna, no matter what,
don't move away from me!

158
00:12:50,234 --> 00:12:52,168
Yeah... I soo know it!

159
00:12:56,641 --> 00:12:58,541
<i>I know...</i>
<i>Zabuza...</i>

160
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:01,207
<i>I'll finish them off soon enough...</i>

161
00:13:05,850 --> 00:13:07,841
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

162
00:13:11,055 --> 00:13:12,545
You just don't learn, do you?!

163
00:13:20,098 --> 00:13:21,531
<i>What? The Fire Style Jutsu!</i>

164
00:13:30,942 --> 00:13:33,240
<i>It takes...too long!</i>

165
00:14:08,212 --> 00:14:09,372
<i>This is good!</i>

166
00:14:09,447 --> 00:14:11,779
<i>Bit by bit, I'm figuring out</i>
<i>the timing...</i>

167
00:14:22,994 --> 00:14:25,758
<i>I know it's called Hidden Mist,</i>
<i>but the fog is way too thick...</i>

168
00:14:26,764 --> 00:14:29,255
<i>Even Zabuza himself shouldn't</i>
<i>be able to see anything...</i>

169
00:14:37,074 --> 00:14:38,564
Good job on dodging it...

170
00:14:39,110 --> 00:14:41,101
Just what I expect of Kakashi
of the Sharingan...

171
00:14:47,752 --> 00:14:48,684
<i>He's...</i>

172
00:14:48,853 --> 00:14:49,751
<i>closing his eyes!</i>

173
00:14:50,588 --> 00:14:53,022
But... the next time you see me,

174
00:14:53,424 --> 00:14:55,289
that'll be the end of it all...

175
00:14:55,993 --> 00:14:59,019
You overrate the Sharingan too much.

176
00:14:59,096 --> 00:14:59,960
What...?

177
00:15:01,532 --> 00:15:05,866
You spoke as if you saw through
everything, but...

178
00:15:10,241 --> 00:15:11,333
<i>Why?</i>

179
00:15:12,543 --> 00:15:15,979
<i>Could it be possible that</i>
<i>you can see the future...?!</i>

180
00:15:19,283 --> 00:15:20,807
<i>You are going to die.</i>

181
00:15:21,185 --> 00:15:24,586
Your foresight was wrong, after all.

182
00:15:25,523 --> 00:15:26,490
Kakashi...

183
00:15:26,924 --> 00:15:30,360
You can't read my mind or
my future...

184
00:15:30,995 --> 00:15:34,931
The Sharingan is merely a diversion
that makes you believe that!

185
00:15:36,734 --> 00:15:38,861
Those who have the Sharingan...

186
00:15:39,203 --> 00:15:43,867
possess both
perceptive eyes and hypnotic eyes...

187
00:15:47,411 --> 00:15:51,279
Using these two powers and
bringing out Jutsus one after the other...

188
00:15:52,049 --> 00:15:56,748
you were just acting as if
you can read the future!

189
00:15:59,991 --> 00:16:04,018
First with the perceptive eyes,
you copied my movement right away.

190
00:16:05,296 --> 00:16:07,856
And this is the Image
Replication Method.

191
00:16:14,238 --> 00:16:16,763
You first got me in
a ruffle with it...

192
00:16:17,141 --> 00:16:19,974
Once you make sure that
I'm flustered,

193
00:16:20,044 --> 00:16:24,276
you nail the "heart's voice."

194
00:16:25,116 --> 00:16:27,880
- This is the Mind Imitation Method.
- <i>It's only an imitation, after all.</i>

195
00:16:28,653 --> 00:16:32,350
- <i>You can't defeat me! You monkey!</i>
- <i>You can't defeat me! You monkey!</i>

196
00:16:33,391 --> 00:16:35,359
<i>That imitating monkey mouth...</i>

197
00:16:35,426 --> 00:16:37,553
<i>I'll make sure that you won't be</i>
<i>able to open it any more!</i>

198
00:16:37,962 --> 00:16:38,758
And...

199
00:16:38,829 --> 00:16:42,026
You judged the right timing when
my frustration was reaching its height

200
00:16:42,533 --> 00:16:43,431
<i>W-What is that?</i>

201
00:16:44,001 --> 00:16:46,731
You set a clever trap.

202
00:16:47,271 --> 00:16:48,203
<i>Me...?</i>

203
00:16:48,839 --> 00:16:50,966
You used the Genjutsu with
your hypnotic eye and

204
00:16:51,042 --> 00:16:55,206
made me weave the signs first...

205
00:16:56,581 --> 00:16:59,516
This is the Jutsu Imitation Method...

206
00:16:59,650 --> 00:17:02,084
<i>The Giant Vortex Jutsu!</i>

207
00:17:13,030 --> 00:17:14,292
<i>R-Ridiculous!</i>

208
00:17:17,535 --> 00:17:19,435
Then that makes it easier.

209
00:17:20,438 --> 00:17:23,168
First vanish into the thick fog,

210
00:17:23,474 --> 00:17:25,942
and make your
perceptive eyes useless...

211
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:27,135
<i>Huh?</i>

212
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:32,007
<i>Darn! The guard is falling behind!</i>

213
00:17:32,683 --> 00:17:35,709
I will close my eyes as well!

214
00:17:36,754 --> 00:17:40,190
I will shut off your ability to use
your hypnotic eye

215
00:17:40,257 --> 00:17:41,918
in a close distance battle.

216
00:17:43,728 --> 00:17:44,820
Why?

217
00:17:45,162 --> 00:17:47,596
That also means that
you will lose your ability to see.

218
00:17:48,599 --> 00:17:50,066
Did you forget?

219
00:17:50,935 --> 00:17:53,836
That I am a genius in Silent Killing,

220
00:17:54,038 --> 00:17:58,839
a technique to find
the target just by sound.

221
00:18:05,182 --> 00:18:08,811
<i>He read my movement...</i>
<i>No way could he do that.</i>

222
00:18:10,054 --> 00:18:12,716
Darn! We were so close!

223
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:15,315
Naruto, can you still move?

224
00:18:15,793 --> 00:18:18,728
Of course! I'm totally fine!

225
00:18:19,463 --> 00:18:22,660
<i>He's pretty much spent...</i>
<i>and it's no wonder.</i>

226
00:18:22,967 --> 00:18:25,765
<i>Shadow Clone Jutsu uses</i>
<i>a lot of Chakra.</i>

227
00:18:26,437 --> 00:18:28,667
<i>But thanks to him,</i>
<i>I found our way out.</i>

228
00:18:29,473 --> 00:18:30,963
<i>I found the way to break through!</i>

229
00:18:32,376 --> 00:18:34,344
<i>Hah! Impossible!</i>

230
00:18:36,514 --> 00:18:39,677
<i>That was just a coincidence.</i>

231
00:18:43,621 --> 00:18:44,781
Naruto! Run!

232
00:18:44,855 --> 00:18:45,583
What?

233
00:18:45,690 --> 00:18:48,090
Run out of here and
attack from the outside!

234
00:18:49,260 --> 00:18:50,921
A-All right!

235
00:18:52,997 --> 00:18:54,328
You won't be able to.!

236
00:19:06,977 --> 00:19:08,274
I-I'm not going to lose!

237
00:19:11,515 --> 00:19:12,379
There!

238
00:19:12,450 --> 00:19:14,475
Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!

239
00:19:40,611 --> 00:19:42,010
Darn!

240
00:19:43,414 --> 00:19:44,642
T-That was good just now!

241
00:19:44,782 --> 00:19:45,646
What?

242
00:19:46,250 --> 00:19:47,945
We're doing it one more time!

243
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,619
All right!

244
00:19:54,125 --> 00:19:57,094
<i>It's likely that there's a limit</i>
<i>to that guy's Chakra, too!</i>

245
00:19:58,596 --> 00:20:00,154
<i>To prove that,</i>
<i>he's little by little...</i>

246
00:20:06,237 --> 00:20:08,671
This won't go as you've planned.

247
00:20:09,907 --> 00:20:11,397
First, I'll get you!

248
00:20:17,548 --> 00:20:18,446
Sasuke!

249
00:20:27,525 --> 00:20:32,155
<i>Darn! It's been a while since</i>
<i>I've fought in such bad conditions.</i>

250
00:20:33,964 --> 00:20:36,330
<i>And I'm worried about</i>
<i>Sasuke and Naruto, too...</i>

251
00:20:40,638 --> 00:20:46,372
<i>Be calm... Think...</i>
<i>What will he come after?</i>

252
00:20:47,778 --> 00:20:48,676
<i>Oh no!</i>

253
00:21:04,295 --> 00:21:05,193
What?!

254
00:21:05,763 --> 00:21:06,695
Too late!

255
00:22:53,039 --> 00:22:55,769
Why? Why is it?

256
00:22:56,343 --> 00:22:58,709
Why did this happen?

257
00:22:59,312 --> 00:23:05,842
I never asked for your help!
I hated you!

258
00:23:06,453 --> 00:23:07,613
But you...

259
00:23:08,955 --> 00:23:12,823
Darn! I won't forgive you!

260
00:23:13,994 --> 00:23:16,986
Next episode:
"The Broken Seal"
